                        <interp inst="t18430102-471-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 32.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy by the Jury and Prosecutor.</hi>
               </p>
